2.  Use by any charitable organization, educational institution, public
    research organization, public safety or health organization,
    environmental protection organization, or government institution.

3.  Use for the benefit of the public good.

4.  Seeking approval for any of the above uses.

Noncommercial Purposes include any purpose that meets ALL of the
following:

a.  Commercial advantage or private monetary compensation is not the
    primary purpose or goal.

b.  No commercial product or service is being marketed, sold, or
    provided using the software.

c.  Use is internal to an organization and not made available as a
